com.vector.cfg.gen.core.bswmdmodel

Interface GIReferenceToContainer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GIModelObject, GIParamOrRef, GIReference<com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.model.autosar.ecucdescription.MIContainer>, IViewedModelObject
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    GISymbolicNameReference
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GSymbolicNameReference

    @NotThreadSafe
 @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
public interface GIReferenceToContainer
extends GIReference<com.vector.cfg.model.mdf.model.autosar.ecucdescription.MIContainer>
    Base interface of bswmd model references which point to a GIContainer.
    The following references are references to container (References pointing to container) and are subtypes of the GIReferenceToContainer.
    • Normal Reference
    • SymbolicNameReference
    • ChoiceReference

    References have the method getRefTarget(), which returns the target as BswmdModel object, if the type is known at model generation time, the type will be the generated type. Otherwise the return type is GIContainer.

    Note: It is always allowed to call getRefTarget(), also for references pointing to external types.

    All method parameters must be non-null unless documented otherwise.
